# circleci_organization (Resource)

Manages a CircleCI organization.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "circleci_organization" "example" {
  name     = "my-org"
  vcs_type = "github"
}
```

{{ .SchemaMarkdown | trimspace }}

## Import

Import is supported using the organization ID:

```shell
terraform import circleci_organization.example "<organization_id>"
```
